room_title: Escape room "The Law Breakers" by No Escape Room in Chicago

room_description: You have just managed to escape from the police station with all the money. For now, you are free but you need to clear your tracks to get rid of all the evidence against you. Your partner tried to retrieve it while you were locked up, but he's gone missing. Can you find the evidence to clear your good name?
